**concerns**:
- Inline styles on the save pane/buttons in `builder.css` — the CSS file wasn't in the allowlist, so styles were inlined in `builder.html`. A future cleanup pass should move these to `builder.css`.
- After save+reopen, all tray rows show as "deck" kind (including former blanks/library slides). This is correct behavior — recompose writes all items as `<section>` elements, and the deck loader treats every `<section>` as an existing slide. The test was adjusted to assert count=12 rather than mixed kinds.

